parameters: Do you want to enter the boss area?
Clea (Let's prepare first before doing that)
Clea: They should be ahead, let's go.
Former Tomosu Plunder Squad Funnel: Welcome to our hideout

Former Tomosu Plunder Squad Funnel: The adventurer's guild
is welcome here... but it seems like I don't remember any of
these people.
Former Tomosu Plunder Squad Funnel: Miss, what is your name?

Clea: I am Clea, a member of the Adventurer's Guild, Futera
branch.

Former Tomosu Plunder Squad Funnel: Wearing a green cloak
means that at least you are recognized by Agonia.

Former Tomosu Plunder Squad Funnel: We call ourselves the
Former Tomosu Plunder Squad.
Former Tomosu Plunder Squad Funnel: Do you know why?

Clea: I have no interest. Just the fact that you are enemies
of the guild is enough.

Former Tomosu Plunder Squad Funnel: Hey, at least listen to
what I have to say, old man.

Former Tomosu Plunder Squad Funnel: Can you believe it,
Agonia and Shimos came to our hideout that day, just the two
of them.

Former Tomosu Plunder Squad Funnel: After that, they started
killing without any hesitation or hesitation, it's a
terrible thing.

Former Tomosu Plunder Squad Funnel: The reason is that they
desecrated the grave of the former guild leader--

Receptionist Piste: Ah, it was you guys! That place is a
sacred location for us!

Former Tomosu Plunder Squad Funnel: But even so! It's not a
valid reason to kill 80% of our members, you know!?

Former Tomosu Plunder Squad Funnel: We will crush the
adventurer's guild that took away our pride and return to
the Tomosu Plunder Squad!

Former Tomosu Plunder Squad Funnel: First, I'll send the
head of the woman who talked back earlier to the guild.

Clea: I may not understand the deep circumstances, but I
won't let Piste-san or the Adventurer's Guild get hurt.
Clea: Piste-san, please step back. I'm going to go all out.

Former Tomosu Plunder Squad Funnel: No matter how many
times... no matter how much we're laughed at for being
pathetic... I will reclaim our pride...

Former Tomosu Plunder Squad Funnel: As long as I'm here...
the Tomosu Plunder Squad will never end!
Stolge the Merciful: No, it ends here.

Former Tomosu Plunder Squad Funnel: You... you're really
persistent... hahaha... you monsters... more than us small-
time thugs...

Stolge the Merciful: The Adventurer's Guild will surely
retaliate. You have desecrated the tomb of a great widow.

Stolge the Merciful: For us in the Adventurer's Guild,
whether they're alive or dead, everyone is a comrade.
Clea: Thank you very much, Stolge-san.

Clea: I apologize if I misunderstood, but did you happen to
follow us to the village of Alkay?

Stolge the Merciful: I thought I was being careful, moving
downwind so Nora wouldn't notice, but... well, I guess
not...

Stolge the Merciful: I should honestly praise you for
this.

Receptionist Piste: Well then, why did you come at such a
good timing?

Stolge the Merciful: It's just a coincidence, but probably
the same as Piste.

Stolge the Merciful: I also felt like coming back after a
long time to that place I visited with the great widow.

Receptionist Piste: Oh, I see. In that case, I'll guide
Clea-chan and the others too!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Former Tomosu Plunder Gang Funnel: Well, what are you going
to do?
Receptionist Piste: W-Well, as for me...

Former Tomosu Plunder Gang Funnel: Hehe, there aren't any
choices, though.

Former Tomosu Plunder Gang Funnel: There are four of our
comrades on the brink of death, but we still have five of us
who can keep going.

Former Tomosu Plunder Gang Funnel: Hey, take off your
clothes.

Former Tomosu Plunder Gang Funnel: Obey my orders
immediately. Every time you show a disrespectful attitude, I
will kill one of you.

Former Tomosu Plunder Gang Funnel: If you obediently follow
my orders, I promise that we won't take the lives of the
four of you.

Former Tomosu Plunder Gang Funnel: I'll say it one more
time. Take off your clothes here and entertain us.
Would you like to skip the adult scene?

Would you like to retry the battle? If you choose No, it
will result in a game over.
